data.description: Haymount 1.5-Story Cottage-style residence offers 4 BRs, 3 BAs, & a finished Bonus Rm with an elongated wet bar. Completely renovated late 2021, & multiple enhancements 2023, served as an income-generating short-term rental. Property features beautiful HWD floors, carpeting, & spacious tiled floors throughout. Expansive kitchen is a sight to behold, perfect for culinary delights & aesthetic pleasure. Primary suite & two additional BR are conveniently located on the 1st floor boasting stunning tiled walls & granite countertops in the bathrooms. The 2nd floor provides an ideal space for guests, or secondary primary suite complete with a BR, Full BA, & living area. Backyard offers ample room for community gatherings & extra parking. Just minutes away from downtown Fayetteville's Segra Stadium, museums, & more, with a charming playground & community park nearby for families with young children. Sellers are open to help towards buyer closing costs with accepted offer.
